<h3 id="mdppolicy">MDP+Policy</h3>

<ul>
  <li>MDP + $\pi(a|s)$ = Markov Reward process
\(R^{\pi}(s) = \sum_{a\in A}\pi(a|s)R(s,a)
\\ P^\pi(s^`|s) = \sum_{a\in A}\pi(a|s)P(s^`|s,a)\)</li>
  <li>in this way, we can see MDP as MRP</li>
  <li>
    <p>Iterative Algorithm
\(V^{\pi}_k(s) =  r(s,\pi(s)) + \gamma\sum_{s^`\in S}p(s^`|s,\pi (s))V^{\pi}_{k-1}(s^`)\)</p>

    <ul>
      <li>this is called Bellman backup</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

